{"title":"歙砚","authors":["陈所巨"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":7,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"歙砚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈所巨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"切龙尾山石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"切大大小小的长方正方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"切许些许些神肖形似的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蟠龙卧虎伏牛蹲蛙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"切好些桑叶荷团"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与献寿的双果"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑如朔夜的石头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细腻如肌肤的石头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"复活动静，以古歙州灵气"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻巧地翻手为云覆手为雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后，以石头的语言复述"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辉煌荣耀与辛酸旧事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后，再以一汪清水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再以一顶香墨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再以一注文彩神思"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"慢慢磨砺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古今文章"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和沉重的二十四史……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}